OL,3,CWhat are the new Congestion Charge
OL,4,Cfees, for which vehicles and how to
OL,5,Cpay?
OL,7,FDrivers going through central London
OL,8,Fwill have to pay an increased
OL,9,FCongestion Charge fee from 2026.
OL,11,FThe new prices will see the charge
OL,12,Fincrease for all different vehicle
OL,13,Ftypes, but there are some discounts
OL,14,Favailable for electric vehicles.
OL,16,FMayor of London, Sadiq Khan said:
OL,17,F"Keeping London moving by reducing
OL,18,Fcongestion is vital for our city and
OL,19,Ffor our economy.
