OL,3,CWhat are the new Congestion Charge
OL,4,Cfees, for which vehicles and how to
OL,5,Cpay?
OL,7,F"While the congestion charge has been
OL,8,Fa huge success since its introduction,
OL,9,Fwe must ensure it stays fit for
OL,10,Fpurpose, and sticking to the status
OL,11,Fquo would see around 2,200 more
OL,12,Fvehicles using the congestion charging
OL,13,Fzone on an average weekday next year. "
OL,15,FHere's a breakdown of the new prices
OL,16,Fand everything drivers need to know
OL,17,Fbefore they come into place.
