OL,3,CWhat are the new Congestion Charge
OL,4,Cfees, for which vehicles and how to
OL,5,Cpay?
OL,7,FThe daily Congestion Charge will
OL,8,Fincrease from #15 to #18.
OL,10,FWhen do the new prices come in?
OL,12,FThe price hike begins on January, 2,
OL,13,F2026.
OL,15,FFour years later, there is second
OL,16,Fphase on 4 March 2030 which will
OL,17,Freduce discounts for electric vehicles.
