OL,3,CWhat are the new Congestion Charge
OL,4,Cfees, for which vehicles and how to
OL,5,Cpay?
OL,7,FThe charges run from Monday to Friday
OL,8,Ffrom 7am to 6pm and from midday to 6pm
OL,9,Fon Saturdays, Sundays and bank
OL,10,Fholidays. There is no charge between
OL,11,FChristmas Day and New Year's Day bank
OL,12,Fholiday.
OL,14,FWhat discounts can I get?
OL,16,FFrom 2 January 2026, there will be two
OL,17,Ftiers of discounts. All vehicles must
OL,18,Fbe registered for TFL's Auto Pay
OL,19,Fsystem, which will be explained below.
