OL,3,CWhat are the new Congestion Charge
OL,4,Cfees, for which vehicles and how to
OL,5,Cpay?
OL,7,FThere is a 50 per cent discount for
OL,8,Felectric vans, HGVs and quadricycles
OL,9,Fif registered to Auto Pay. From 4
OL,10,FMarch 2030 this will be reduced to 25
OL,11,Fper cent.
OL,13,FThere is a 25 per cent discount for
OL,14,Felectric cars if registered Auto Pay.
OL,15,FFrom 4 March 2030 this will be reduced
OL,16,Fto 12.5 per cent.
OL,18,FCurrently, there is a 100 per cent
OL,19,Fexemption for drivers of electric
OL,20,Fvehicles.
