OL,3,CWhat are the new Congestion Charge
OL,4,Cfees, for which vehicles and how to
OL,5,Cpay?
OL,7,FResidents Discount
OL,9,FThere is also the Residents' Discount
OL,10,Fwhich gives 90 per cent off to people
OL,11,Fwho live in the Congestion Charge zone.
OL,13,FPeople who get the Residents' Discount
OL,14,Fbefore to March, 1, 2027 will retain
OL,15,Ftheir 90 per cent discount, regardless
OL,16,Fof vehicle fuel type.
OL,18,FFor those applying for the Residents'
OL,19,FDiscount after 1 March 2027, the 90
OL,20,Fper cent discount will only apply to
OL,21,FElectric Vehicles.
