OL,4,Cfees, for which vehicles and how to
OL,5,Cpay?
OL,7,FWhat is Auto Pay?
OL,9,FDrivers can set up Auto Pay via the
OL,10,FTransport for London website.
OL,12,FIt means they will automatically
OL,13,Fcharge drivers when they go through
OL,14,Fthe payable zones.
